title: Jeffrey Epstein co-conspirator Ghislaine Maxwell to testify before Congress
description: Jeffrey Epstein co-conspirator Ghislaine Maxwell will sit Monday for closed-door, virtual testimony with lawmakers on the Republican-led House Oversight Committee.
